1085
01:25:00,679 --> 01:25:02,054
God damn it.

1086
01:25:02,890 --> 01:25:05,224
You take care of yourself, okay?

1087
01:25:08,270 --> 01:25:09,937
I'm gonna make it.

1088
01:25:20,491 --> 01:25:21,783
What about Entrekin?

1089
01:25:21,867 --> 01:25:24,744
I don't know. He hasn't returned
