1158
01:30:44,397 --> 01:30:48,234
If you have any means of getting
away from the path of this wave,

1159
01:30:48,318 --> 01:30:49,652
leave now.

1160
01:30:50,278 --> 01:30:52,530
The impact of the larger comet

1161
01:30:52,864 --> 01:30:56,158
will be nothing less than
